nodes.text: Kase Finto was a male individual who led the Finto Gang. Finto tried to sell fake Lothal gemstones to Dok-Ondar in Black Spire Outpost on Batuu, but the collector's IG droid BK-86 drew its blaster on him. His attempt at scamming Dok-Ondar resulted in a shootout, which ended with Finto dead and BK-86 destroyed.
